  "body": "to extend https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/14334\r\n\r\n* [ ] implement SegmentWriter interface for BMT hash \r\n* [ ] implement getting inclusion proofs and validation\r\n\r\n```golang\r\ntype SegmentWriter interface {\r\n\tInit(int) // initialises the segment writer with max int chunks\r\n\tWriteSegment(int, []byte) error // ability to write segments concurrrently\r\n\tHash() []byte // get the result\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```golang\r\nfunc (b *Hasher) SegmentProof(index int) ([][]byte, error) {\r\n  // error if b is not finalised or index out of range\r\n  // return list of neighbour hashes for the bmt proof of segment with index \r\n}\r\n\r\nfunc ValidateProof(hash []byte, segmentCount, index int, proof ...[]byte) error {\r\n // returns nil iff segment of index and neighbour hashes of proof constitute a valid bmt proof\r\n // against root hash  of a chunk with segmentCount segments\r\n}\r\n\r\n```",
